#: src-ru/data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber:249
msgid "data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ROCK_LOOTING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你发现一艘报废的岩石族运输船漂浮在信标附近。你打算带走所有有用的零件，但不知"
"道在你之前它在这里做过什么。"

#: src-ru/data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber:251
msgid ""
"data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ROCK_LOOTING\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "搜刮飞船。"

#: src-ru/data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber:255
msgid ""
"data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ROCK_LOOTING\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不管他。"

#: src-ru/data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber:259
msgid ""
"data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ROCK_LOOTING\"]/choice[@req=\"slug_crew\"]/text"
msgstr "（蛞蝓族船员）检查是否存在生命体征，并在搜索飞船残骸时保持警惕。"

#: src-ru/data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber:265
msgid ""
"data/events_rock.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ROCK_LOOTING_STRIP\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr "你从飞船上收集了所有能拿的东西。操作期间无人打扰。"

